  "detailed_description": "Raey Ragnos is a young warrior from the barbarian village of Umbridge. His brother Richter dreams of being a great warrior.  <br />\r\nUmbridge is surrounded by warring tribes all trying to take what the family has built.<br />\r\nEmbark on the journey and watch his eventful life unfold before your eyes.<br />\r\nFrom the cradle to the grave - Raey will take the player through a roller coaster of emotions as he endures everything that is thrown at him.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nRaey is a classic single player RPG with modern elements included such as skill level ups and a Veteran Experience System to develop characters.",
